          <p>We may allow third-party service providers to place cookies on our website for analytics, marketing, and advertising purposes. These third-party cookies enable us to track user activity and display relevant advertisements based on your interests. We do not control the use of these cookies and encourage you to review the privacy policies of any third-party services you interact with.</p>
          <p>
            <span style="font-weight: 700;">Managing Cookies</span>
          </p>
          <p>You have the right to manage your cookie preferences. Most web browsers allow you to accept or decline cookies through their settings. You can also delete cookies that have already been placed on your device. However, please note that disabling or deleting certain cookies may impact the functionality of our website and limit your access to some features.</p>
          <p>
            <span style="font-weight: 700;">How Long Do Cookies Last</span>
          </p>
          <p>Cookies can vary in duration. Session cookies expire when you close your browser, while persistent cookies may remain on your device for a specified period or until you delete them. The duration of each cookie can be found in your browser settings or by reviewing the specific cookies used on our site.</p>
